  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Thread cheese, sausage, bell peppers, onions, and bread slices onto skewers.",
    "3. Brush olive oil onto skewers.",
    "4. Season with garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "5. Grill skewers for 2-3 minutes per side, or until cheese is melted and bread is toasted.",
    "6. Serve immediately with chimichurri sauce, if desired."
